ze: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; background-color: var(--black-075); white-space: pre-wrap; color: var(--black-800); border-radius: 3px;\">git merge</code>.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--s-prose-spacing); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\">You can do a&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; background-color: var(--black-075); white-space: pre-wrap; color: var(--black-800); border-radius: 3px;\">git fetch</code>&nbsp;at any time to update your remote-tracking branches under&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; background-color: var(--black-075); white-space: pre-wrap; color: var(--black-800); border-radius: 3px;\">refs/remotes/&lt;remote&gt;/</code>.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--s-prose-spacing); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; clear: both; color: rgb(36, 39, 41);\">This operation never changes any of your own local branches under&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; background-color: var(--black-075); white-space: pre-wrap; color: var(--black-800); border-radius: 3px;\">refs/heads</code>, and is safe to do without changing your working copy. I have even heard of people running&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 4px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; background-color: var(--black-075); white-space: pre-wrap; color: var(--black-800); border-radius: 3px;\">git fetch</code>&nbsp;periodically in a cron job in the background (although I wouldn\'t recommend doing this).</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--s-prose-spacing); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; clear: both; color