(22, 'What is Inheritance?', 'shubham@gmail.com', '<p>I had doubt regarding the concept of inheritance.</p>', 'shreevadan10@gmail.com', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 89, 104); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Inheritance is property in which the property of a parent class(Superclass) is passed on to child class(Subclass). For example</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 89, 104); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 89, 104); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">class Abc{ —– This is a class</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 89, 104); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 89, 104); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">int a; —— This is a variable</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 89, 104); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 89, 104); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">public void abc(){} — Methods</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 89, 104); 